Package com.sun.identity.saml.protocol

Provides interface to construct and process SAML request-response protocol.

          Description

Class Summary
AbstractRequest This AbstractRequest class is an abstract base class for all SAML Request in samlp namespace.
AbstractResponse This AbstractResponse class is an abstract base class for all SAML Response in samlp namespace.
AssertionArtifact This class represents the AssertionArtifact element in SAML protocol schema.
AttributeQuery This concrete class extends from the abstract base class SubjectQuery.
AuthenticationQuery This concrete class extends from the abstract base class SubjectQuery.
AuthorizationDecisionQuery This concrete class extends from the abstract base class SubjectQuery.
Query This is an abstract base class for SAML query.
Request This Request class represents a Request XML document.
Response This Response class represents a Response XML document.
Status This class represents the Status element.
StatusCode This class represents the StatusCode and SubStatusCode element.
SubjectQuery This abstract class extends from another abstract class Query.
